An eight-year-old boy fired a gunshot which left his five-year-old relative with serious facial injuries, police have confirmed today.

Officers were called to a house in Wickford, Essex, on Sunday following reports that a firearm had been discharged.

They believe the shooting, which took place at around 1pm, was an accident.

